						nonpublic school provided the notification required pursuant to paragraph (1).</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(m) (1) Notwithstanding any other law, the Superintendent shall not certify or renew the certification of a nonpublic school that also operates a licensed children’s institution, unless all of the following conditions are met:</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 2.5em;">(A) The entity operating the nonpublic
